Package de.linearbits.objectselector Description

This package provides the public API for Object Selector.

  • The interface IAccessor can be implemented to enable selection of objects.
  • The interface ICallback can be implemented and passed to a SelectorTokenizer.
  • The class Parser parses expressions created with the builder.
  • The class Selectorrepresents the actual selector.
  • The class SelectorBuilder implements a builder for selectors
  • The class SelectorBuilderCallback is a callback used by the builder when parsing query strings
  • The class SelectorTokenizer is a tokenizer for query strings
